overview_description.description: AMPnet provides every new or existing cooperative with a full set of tools to manage payments, invoicing, , smart metering, demand side management, crowdinvesting and community governance. AMPnet is an integrated hardware and software suite comprised of web applications, iOS & Android apps, blockchain payments and governance platform and an open source smart meter hardware specification. We provide a simple turnkey solution - reducing onboarding complexity and operating costs.

about_short_description.short_description: AMPnet is a financing platform and marketplace for renewable energy sources - making renewables viable for a new class of investors.

product.name: TokenHub
product.description: A platform for launching tokens on EVM-compatible networks, facilitating direct sales and brokerage of ERC20 tokens.

product.name: Asset Studio
product.description: A tool for creating digital asset issuance and management platforms, decentralized exchanges, or custodial wallets without coding.

product.name: Custom Solution
product.description: A service where AMPnet designs and builds custom digital asset solutions based on client needs.

product.name: Digital Assets for Emissions Trading
product.description: Enables creation of unified markets for emissions trading and customer engagement through retail offsetting schemes.

product.name: Fractional Asset Ownership
product.description: Allows investors to fractionally purchase shares of equity assets or invest in lending contracts, supporting large numbers of investors.

product.name: Loyalty Schemes with Digital Assets
product.description: Enables brands to create loyalty programs connected to data collection, and sports clubs to engage fans and offer rewards.
